dc_description_s: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Depths shown by isobaths and soundings. Military topographic map showing numbered government, military, transportation, and industrial facilities. "Sostavleno po karte masshtaba 1:25 000 izd. 1961-75 gg. s ispolʹzovaniem materialov na 1980-81 gg." In Russian. "Sistema koordinat 1942 g." "Spravka, perechenʹ nazvaniĭ ulit︠s︡ i perechenʹ vazhnykh obʺektov izdany otdelʹnoĭ broshi︠u︡roĭ." Includes sheet index diagram. Sheets are : List 1 -- List 2. Former security classification in margin: Sekretno.
